strings: <voice_0x01001047><se_def>*: What are you doing here, not heresy!
<voice_0x01001048><se_def>*: Rollo, the high priest! Marcelo Director!
<voice_0x01001049><se_low>Lulu's priestess: This is the holy island of Neos! papal coronation
<voice_0x0100104A><se_low>Lulu's priestess: You could become the leader of the Templars. But a humble person like you will not be able to last.
<voice_0x0100104B><se_low>Lulu's priestess: Do you know Marcelo? Your obligation to continue to maintain is not a privilege.
<voice_0x0100104C><se_low>Lulu's priestess: Of course, I'm the only one who knows which side you're on about the high priest.
<voice_0x0100104D><se_low>Lulu's priestess: like the rest he always takes special care of me.
<voice_0x0100104E><se_def>awesome!: ...Yes, of course I know the high priest's duties.
<voice_0x0100104F><se_low>Lulu's priestess: and without our advice you will not be treated as a man of your age.
<voice_0x01001050><se_low>Lulu's priestess: save it!
<voice_0x01001051><se_def>awesome!: High Priestess, I express my gratitude and devotion to my future country.
<voice_0x01001052><se_def>awesome!: ... One day, a merchant brought us to a temple with precious stones.
<voice_0x01001053><se_low>Lulu's priestess: You are always interested in many things, aren't you? However, Marcelo!
<voice_0x01001054><se_low>Lulu's priestess: The Pope participated in the ceremony. No cunning in the world can beat him!
<voice_0x01001055><se_low>Lulu's priestess: But this time, daughter, forgive your mistake. Hand over the jewelry and don't talk about it anymore.
<voice_0x01001056><se_low>Lulu's priestess: Let's get it done! Let us go home
<voice_0x01001057><se_def>awesome!: ...Very well! it is a rare gem!
<voice_0x01001058><se_def>awesome!: Who's less religious than you?
<voice_0x01001059><se_def>awesome!: Why don't you ask a wise man for help or advice? Email Purpose<:> Hmm! how simple life is!
<voice_0x0100105B><se_def>awesome!: ... absolutely free! Too busy to worry about you.
<voice_0x0100105C><se_def>awesome!: I have to thank everyone
<voice_0x0100105D><se_def>awesome!: Take a break. But don't forget the people who will evaluate the grant!
<se_def>*: Do you know Marcelo? Rules are rules though.
<se_def>*: Appears! I'm not letting you in!
